ed with the best Mac DVD burning software.","This application has a drag-and-drop feature to make it easier to highlight and include the video you need to burn. You can also adjust the speed of the burn to ensure the highest quality of your burned disc. shadowBurn is capable of burning content onto DVD-R(W) and DVD+ R discs and dual-layer DVDs. This means your finished DVD can be played on most standard video players. It also means you can copy content onto rewritable discs that can be erased and reused later.","Some functions that shadowBurn lack are the ability to create labels for your discs and including menus for your movies. It also will not break through CSS decryptions or region codes of copyrighted DVDs, so you won&#39;t be able to back up your commercial DVDs. It cannot copy damaged discs either, a feature found on the top-ranked Mac DVD burning applications.","Downloading and using shadowBurn is fairly straightforward. The interface is simple to navigate, partially because of the lack of advanced features. However, if you need extra support, stupidFish23 has both email and telephone support available, and some user forums if you would like to browse through questions that have already been asked and answered, or post your own."]},"id":"3e79787b-649e-49be-a491-75a8593cd5b9","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"1b3f980d-99f3-471a-a232-87879ca3c504","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["shadowBurn isn&#39;t the top Mac DVD burning software available. It lacks features that help create memorable movies, such as support for menus and the ability to copy damaged discs. It is effective in burning discs in formats that are readable on most standard video players. It can also burn audio files and CDs. While it isn&#39;t the most advanced application, its basic functions are enough for many tasks."]},"id":"cee426f9-942f-4e5b-896b-d11b6c17bd99","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_59344","url":"/shadowburn-review","authors":[{"